B.RS=s(["Always consolidate carts.","Always have someone scrubbing and moving things through the sinks.","Spray sheet pans over the drain, and utilize the pan machine. Always have it going with dishes in it.","When you have more hands, use them to scrub rice pans and other dishes with stubborn food.","Take care of raw meat dishes quickly.","If you have no dishes to clean, check Main Dish, the serving lines, and the Island."],t.s)
