B.ab1=new A.ci("Tips and Tricks","To inform your crew of some tips and tricks that they might be missing out on that could potentially make their life easier.","The ideas are suggestions. You can use them, but come prepared with tips and tricks you have discovered to share with the crew.",B.o,B.Rk)
