B.Rj=s(["Put on disposable gloves before helping someone who is bleeding.","Apply pressure to stop the bleeding.","If it is a minor cut, clean the wound, apply antibiotic, and put on a bandage.","If there is an embedded object, DO NOT PULL IT OUT. Apply pressure with a rolled cloth around it to stop the bleeding.","If there is severe bleeding, call 911.","Wash your hands thoroughly after helping the injured person."],t.s)
B.acn=new A.ad("Bleeding",B.Rj)
B.SD=s(["Keep the body still and stabilize with splint if needed.","If it is a severe fracture, DO NOT MOVE/SET BONES and wait until medical help arrives.","Apply ice packs to prevent swelling."],t.s)
B.abl=new A.ad("Sprain/Fracture",B.SD)
B.U2=s(["First degree (red skin): remove clothing/jewelry from the area, run cool (not cold) water, apply burn gel, and lightly bandage the burn.","Second degree (blisters): same as first degree burn and seek medical attention. Do not break blisters.","Third degree (lack of pain due to nerve damage): call 911 and BYU Security. Safely remove the person from the source of the burn. If it is an electrical burn, make sure power is off before approaching. Check breathing and signs of shock. DO NOT APPLY WATER. Lay the person down, loosely cover the wound with a clean cloth, and raise the burned area."],t.s)
B.abY=new A.ad("Burns",B.U2)
