B.Ud=s(["P-day Clothes: Never let missionaries in P-day clothes into the main cafeteria. Send them to the sack room or to change.","Receipts: Always ask employees and senior missionaries if they would like a receipt.","Closing duties: refill napkins, restock salt/pepper, refill hand sanitizer, take lost and found to front desk, write next meal menu (including hot/fresh bar item), and spot sweep tile floor.","Erasing boards: use a napkin and hand sanitizer, NEVER a rag."],t.s)
B.acz=new A.ad("Main Cashier",B.Ud)
